    {
      "id": "PopularPost330477",
      "post_content": "@Keshiji  \nNot everything appears on the stack, notably, costs. Costs cannot be responded to. As I see it the scenario would play like this: you tap your 2 mana for the [Altar's Reap](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Altar's Reap) and sacrifice the creature, THEN you take the [Altar's Reap](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Altar's Reap) from your hand and put it on the stack. At this point the creature is long gone, and can no longer be sacced to the [Bubbling Cauldron](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Bubbling Cauldron). The case would be similar if you were to use the Cauldron first, since it is a cost that activates the Cauldron's ability. ",
      "posted_by": "Tsagaglalal",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost330477\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">@Keshiji<br/>Not everything appears on the stack, notably, costs. Costs cannot be responded to. As I see it the scenario would play like this: you tap your 2 mana for the <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Altar's Reap\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Altar's Reap\">Altar's Reap</a> and sacrifice the creature, THEN you take the <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Altar's Reap\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Altar's Reap\">Altar's Reap</a> from your hand and put it on the stack. At this point the creature is long gone, and can no longer be sacced to the <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Bubbling Cauldron\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Bubbling Cauldron\">Bubbling Cauldron</a>. The case would be similar if you were to use the Cauldron first, since it is a cost that activates the Cauldron's ability. </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '330477'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy96435\">Tsagaglalal</span>\r\n                                (7/19/2013 12:38:24 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                              